summary: An Ordinance providing for the purchase of a portion of the Northwest one quarter of the Northwest one quarter of the Southwest one quarter (NW 1/4 of NW 1/4 of SW 1/4) of Section Twenty-one (21), Township Twenty-five (25) North, Range Four (4) East W. M., from Henry G. Stoelting, for the purpose of extending and widening East Lynn Street, and appropriating Five Hundred Fifty-five and 15/100 Dollars ($555.15) from the general fund for said purpose.
